Sun International to Sell Stake in Swazispa of Swaziland

-- B y   V u y i s i l e   H l a t h s w a y o
-- 
2011-03-08T08:56:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-08/sun-international-to-sell-stake-in-swazispa-of-swaziland-1-.html
Sun International Ltd. plans to sell
its 50.6 percent stake in  Swazispa Holdings (SWAZISP)  Ltd., a Swaziland
hotels operator, according to a statement published in the
Mbabane-based Times of Swaziland today.  Swazispa owns the Royal Swazi Spa, Lugogo Sun and Ezulwini
Sun in Swaziland.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Vuyisile Hlathswayo in Mbabane at 
 vshlathswayo@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  